segments.text: [SILENCE]  Would you just stay with me? [SILENCE]
Stay with you?
What for? Look at us. We're already fighting. Well, that's what we do. [SILENCE]
We fight.
[SILENCE] You tell me when I'm being an arrogant son of a bitch, and I tell you when you're being a pain in the ass, which you are, 99% of the time.
[SILENCE] I'm not afraid to hurt your feelings. [SILENCE]
They have, like, a two-second rebound rate, and you're back doing the next pain in the ass thing. [SILENCE]
So what?
So it's not gonna be easy. It's gonna be really hard.
[SILENCE]  And we're gonna have to work at this every day, but I wanna do that because I want you. [SILENCE]
I want all of you, forever, you and me, every day. Will you do something for me? [SILENCE]
Please?
[SILENCE] You just picture your life for me. [SILENCE]
30 years from now, 40 years from now, what's it look like? [SILENCE]
If it's with that guy, go. [SILENCE]
Go! I lost you once, I think I could do it again. If I thought it's what you really wanted, [SILENCE]
Don't you take the easy way out.
What easy way?
[SILENCE] There is no easy way. No matter what I do, somebody gets hurt.
Would you stop thinking about what everyone wants? [SILENCE]
Stop thinking about what I want, what he wants, what your parents want. [SILENCE]
What do you want? [SILENCE]
What do you want?
It's not that simple.
What do you want?
[SILENCE] God damn it. What do you want? I have to go. [SILENCE]
